question: Give me all country singers and bluegrass singers who play guitar.
sql_query1:
SELECT Musician.Name 
FROM Musician
WHERE (Musician.Genre = "Country Singer" OR Musician.Genre = "Bluegrass Singer") AND Musician.Instrument = "Guitar"
sql_query2:
SELECT Musician.Name 
FROM Musician
WHERE Musician.Genre = "Country Singer" OR Musician.Genre = "Bluegrass Singer" AND Musician.Instrument = "Guitar"
interpretation1: Show all the country and bluegrass singers who play guitar.
interpretation2: Give me all the country singers, also show the guitar playing bluegrass singers.
